    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains structurally flawless, having undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement. All suspension components maintain factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key vehicle for the purist demanding peak atmospheric performance and structural integrity.",
