    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-condition masterpiece. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its stunning factory finish. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like shine with a professional ceramic coating, free of any chips, scratches, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear, while the original floor mats look as though they\u2019ve never been stepped on. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist technologies, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is indistinguishable from new, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships. It drives with the same precision, power, and smoothness as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a truly pristine example of this model. Non-smoker, no accidents, and includes all original manuals and two keys.",
